entries.alarm_usage: To set an alarm type /alarmAddIn, /alarmAddInRepeat, /alarmAddtAt, or /alarmAddAtRepeat for parameters. Also see the alarm window.
entries.alarm_in_invalid: The specified alarm time is invalid. Valid times for the alarm are 0-8760 hours and 0-60 minutes.
entries.alarm_at_invalid: The specified alarm time is invalid.  Valid times for this alarm are 0-23 for hour and 0-59 for minute.
entries.alarm_maximum_reached: You have reached the maximum of %DI alarms. Please remove an existing alarm to add a new alarm.
